{"type":"message","id":"8258f55b","parentId":"71d4e4b6","timestamp":"2026-04-05T09:58:24.453Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52175c8688a0c4ae716d4a3f6da\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_c4c57a89d2087841ede9f79dce741a07\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_960d65a250c88d28fd58d9ec2f8364d2\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_c4c57a89d2087841ede9f79dce741a07\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-05 17:53 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_960d65a250c88d28fd58d9ec2f8364d2\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_c4c57a89d2087841ede9f79dce741a07\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_c4c57a89d2087841ede9f79dce741a07\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_c4c57a89d2087841ede9f79dce741a07\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b52175c8688a0c4ae716d4a3f6da]\nou_c4c57a89d2087841ede9f79dce741a07: 你好\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_7cf6bec5ca8bd2e29bd2430b7b4c4265\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1775383104449}}
